name: iMax B6AC Pro Balance Charger
description:
This is the latest genuine IMAX Balance Pro charger !! 

The IMAX RC B6AC PRO is a universal dual input AC/DC battery management system. It charges and discharges all the latest battery technologies: LiPo, LiFe, Li-Ion, NiMH, NiCd and even your Pb-batteries can be charged with up to 5A! It handles your racing batteries, receiver packs, your radio and many other battery types. 

SPECIFICATION B6AC pro 
Input voltage: 11-18V DC 100-240V AC 
Charge power: max. 50W 
Discharge power: max. 5W 
Charge current range: 0.1-5.0A 
Discharge current range: 0.1-1.0A

NiCd/NiMH battery cell count: 1-15 cells 
LiPo/LiIo/LiFe battery cell count: 1-6 series

name: Addiktion
description:
Classy and casual infused with an EPIK touch of detail, ADDIKTION was forged from the elements featuring elegant gold and silver metal accents adorning the fashionable and durable polycarbonate frame.

Your vision to the outside world is via a selection of EPIK laser etched ghost, ice or fire mirror lenses each portraying a perception that reflects your unique personality. Thoughtfully designed temple arms now hide the internal durable steel hinges within, providing the perfect mix of form and function.
Whether it's the money, the fame or just living for the EPIK moments, ADDIKTION by EPIK Eyewear is the catalyst to fuel your ADDIKTION.

Features:

Certified UV400 protection
Polycarbonate glossy finish frames
Metal accents coloured in gold or silver
Scratch and shatter resistant mirror lenses
EPIK laser etched lens logo
Internally hidden, durable steel hinges
Named by Dash Anderson via EPIK Eyewear Facebook competition
All EPIK Eyewear frames are polycarbonate
Polycarbonate frames are much more durable and tougher than standard plastic whilst weighing ten times less than glass. EPIK frames are strong enough to stand up to the abuse you throw at them every day.

All EPIK Eyewear lenses offer UV400 protection
You cannot tell how much UV protection a pair of sunglasses will provide simply by their price, colour or by the darkness of the lenses, however all EPIK lenses offer UV400 protection from the sun's harmful ultraviolet rays, which refers to filtering out 99-100% of UVA and UVB light with wavelengths up to 400 nm.

name: TYKE (Kids)
description:
Super tough to withstand everyday wear, TYKE by EPIK Eyewear is designed and sized for children between 1 and 9 years of age.

Large wrap around polycarbonate frames and UV400 laser etched lenses that will protect your child's eyes not only from the sun's harmful ultraviolet rays but also from sharp and small objects during those sugar fueled play sessions.

When it comes to kids we put safety first, and so should you -our polycarbonate frames are so durable that they will not snap! If pushed far enough they will fold in on themselves preventing your child from being exposed to harmful sharp edges, internal hinges ensure that your child will not catch or pinch their curious fingers and non toxic paint is tasty for those children that are still teething.
